title: Number of immigrants in Singapore 2005 to 2019
summary: Overall Number of immigrants in thousands has decreased over the Year.
Number of immigrants in thousands is slightly increasing from 2010 to 2015, roughly constant from 2015 to 2017, and lastly slightly decreasing from 2017 to 2019.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2019.
The highest Number of immigrants in thousands, of value 2623.0 was reached at Year 2017
The lowest Number of immigrants in thousands, of value 2155.65 was reported at Year 2019
